name: Elena
description:
Hey,
My name is Elena and I am a rescued cat living in a individual shelter with a beautiful soul having an eye on me and giving me food and the medications I need.
I love and support stray animals. The sales profit of this collection will be used to support a few individual shelter who does rescue animals. To see some the cats story visit  @6lovely.cats and @edward__angel on Instagram.
